---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: PVC Stabilizer Manufacturer & Supplier
description: Stabplast Chemo Industries Pvt Ltd manufactures PVC stabilizers, metallic stearates and lead compounds for pipes, profiles, cables and plastics. Request a quote today.
---

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero__inner">
    <div class="hero__content">
      <span class="eyebrow hero__eyebrow">Industrial Chemicals · Since {{ site.facts.founded }}</span>
      <h1>Advanced PVC Stabilizers &amp; Additives for Industry</h1>
      <p class="hero__text">
        {{ site.legalName }} manufactures and supplies high-performance stabilizers,
        metallic stearates and lead compounds engineered for pipes, profiles, cables
        and plastic products.
      </p>
      <div class="hero__actions">
        <a class="btn btn--accent btn--lg" href="{{ site.cta.quote.href }}">{{ site.cta.quote.label }}</a>
        <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href="/products/" style="color:#fff;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.6)">Explore Products</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__stats">
        <div class="hero__stat"><b>{{ site.facts.experienceYears }}</b><span>Years of expertise</span></div>
        <div class="hero__stat"><b>3</b><span>Product categories</span></div>
        <div class="hero__stat"><b>B2B</b><span>&amp; Export supply</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__media">
      {% image "src/assets/images/hero-lab.jpg", "Laboratory glassware used in PVC additive quality control", "(max-width: 900px) 90vw, 480px", { loading: "eager", fetchpriority: "high", widths: [480, 800] } %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ WHY US ============ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center">
      <span class="eyebrow">Why Stabplast</span>
      <h2>Consistent quality, reliable supply</h2>
      <p class="lead">Formulations tuned to your process, backed by in-house quality control and dependable lead times.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid--4">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><path d="M12 3l7 4v5c0 5-3 8-7 9-4-1-7-4-7-9V7z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Quality Assured</h3>
        <p>Every batch tested for thermal stability and consistency before dispatch.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 7l9-4 9 4-9 4-9-4z"/><path d="M3 7v6l9 4 9-4V7"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Custom Formulations</h3>
        <p>One-pack and single-stage systems developed to match your application.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M3 12h18M12 3c2.5 2.7 2.5 15 0 18M12 3c-2.5 2.7-2.5 15 0 18"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Export Ready</h3>
        <p>Documentation and packaging suited to domestic and export shipments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature__icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 7L9 18l-5-5"/></svg></div>
        <h3>On-Time Delivery</h3>
        <p>Planned production and stock to keep your line running.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ PRODUCT CATEGORIES ============ -->
<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head section__head--center">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our Range</span>
      <h2>Product categories</h2>
      <p class="lead">A complete portfolio of PVC stabilization and lubrication chemistry.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid--3">
      <a class="card" href="/products/pvc-stabilizers/">
        <div class="card__media">
          {% image "src/assets/images/cat-pvc-stabilizers.jpg", "PVC one-pack stabilizer product", "(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 360px" %}
        </div>
        <div class="card__body">
          <h3 class="card__title">PVC Stabilizers</h3>
          <p>One-pack, single-stage, calcium-zinc and lead-based complex stabilizers.</p>
          <span class="card__link">View category →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="card" href="/products/metallic-stearates/">
        <div class="card__media">
          {% image "src/assets/images/cat-metallic-stearates.jpg", "Calcium stearate metallic stearate powder", "(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 360px" %}
        </div>
        <div class="card__body">
          <h3 class="card__title">Metallic Stearates</h3>
          <p>Calcium, lead and dibasic lead stearate for lubrication and co-stabilization.</p>
          <span class="card__link">View category →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a class="card" href="/products/lead-compounds/">
        <div class="card__media">
          {% image "src/assets/images/cat-lead-compounds.jpg", "Dibasic lead phosphite compound", "(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 360px" %}
        </div>
        <div class="card__body">
          <h3 class="card__title">Lead Compounds</h3>
          <p>Dibasic lead phosphite (DBLP) and tribasic lead sulphate (TBLS).</p>
          <span class="card__link">View category →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ APPLICATIONS ============ -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container hero__inner" style="align-items:center">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Applications</span>
      <h2>Chemistry that performs across industries</h2>
      <p>Our additives are trusted in the manufacture of PVC and CPVC pipes, UPVC window
        and door profiles, wires and cables, masterbatch and a wide range of plastic products.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem"><a class="btn btn--primary" href="/applications/">See all applications</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero__media">
      {% image "src/assets/images/applications.jpg", "Industrial applications of PVC additives", "(max-width: 900px) 90vw, 480px", { widths: [480, 800] } %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ CTA BAND ============ -->
<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container cta-band__inner">
    <div>
      <h2>Ready to discuss your requirement?</h2>
      <p>Tell us your application and volume — we'll recommend the right formulation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-band__actions">
      <a class="btn btn--accent btn--lg" href="{{ site.cta.quote.href }}">{{ site.cta.quote.label }}</a>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href="{{ site.contact.phoneHref }}" style="color:#fff;border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.6)">{{ site.cta.call.label }}</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
